text: Nusret Muslimović (born 25 February 1975) is a Bosnian professional football manager and a former player who is the manager of First League of RS club Jedinstvo Brčko. As a player, he played for Sloboda Tuzla and Bratstvo Gračanica, while as a manager, Muslimović managed Bratstvo, TOŠK Tešanj and since 9 March 2020, Jedinstvo Brčko. ==Managerial statistics== {| class="wikitable" tyle="text-align: center" |+ Managerial record by team and tenure !rowspan="2"|Team !rowspan="2"|From !rowspan="2"|To !colspan="8"|Record |- ! ! ! ! ! ! ! ! |- |align="left"|Bratstvo Gračanica |align="left"|1 July 2012 |align="left"|27 June 2013 |- |align=left|Bratstvo Gračanica |align=left|1 July 2016 |align=left|6 January 2017 |- |align=left|Bratstvo Gračanica |align=left|2 May 2017 |align=left|14 June 2018 |- |align=left|TOŠK Tešanj |align=left|1 July 2019 |align=left|1 September 2019 |- |align=left|Jedinstvo Brčko |align=left|9 March 2020 |align=left|Present |- !colspan="3"|Total |} ==Honours== ===Player=== Bratstvo Gračanica *Second League of FBiH: 2010–11 (North) ==References== ==External links== *Nusret Muslimović at footballdatabase.eu Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Tuzla Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina footballers Category:Premier League of Bosnia and Herzegovina players Category:First League of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina players Category:FK Sloboda Tuzla players Category:Association football defenders Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina football managers Category:NK Bratstvo Gračanica managers Category:NK TOŠK Tešanj managers
